signatureAbility.signatureDescription: Defenders with this ability can still tackle effectively while trying to strip the football.
Passers with this ability have perfect accuracy on all unpressured throws while their feet are set outside the pocket (except on high/low throws).
Passers with this ability have a higher chance of completing a pass animation (and throwing the ball) while being sacked.
Aggressive receivers overpower defenders and attack the football. When they enter the zone, this ability increases their success rate on aggressive catches against single coverage.
Receivers with this ability run sharper routes and catch more consistently while running cross routes.
When lined up at any wide receiver position, players with this ability have access to four additional hot routes during pre-play adjustments.
